            "text": "{\"code\":200,\"msg\":\"success\",\"data\":{\"taskId\":\"11bca28a4b25844533b71709205a1a83\",\"param\":\"Pop, Mysterious\",\"result\":\"Mysterious pop built around a pulsing synth arpeggio, muted electric piano, and tight programmed drums at 104 BPM. Subtle 808 bass, airy pad layers, and echo-drenched plucked guitar add tension. Crisp clap, filtered hi-hats, and reverse FX transitions create a sleek, shadowy gloss with polished vocal harmonies and a hypnotic chorus lift.\",\"creditsConsumed\":0.4,\"creditsRemaining\":110.76,\"successFlag\":\"成功\",\"errorCode\":null,\"errorMsg\":null,\"createTime\":1774788334259}}"
